channel.title: RS2F2P - An attempt at remaking what we all miss
channel.description:
[center][b]Intro[/b][/center] Yes i know there are a lot of remakes out there today and i know that this probably wont get very far, but hey? at least im trying.
[center][b]Goals[/b][/center]
[ul][li]To recreate all of the skills pertaining to the free version of runescape[/li] [li]Make the server compatible with the moparscape client.[/li] [li]Remove all instances of member content[/li] [li]Re-Create most if not all of the free quests[/li] [li]To have an 'economy'[/li] [li]To expand my knowledge of the java programming language[/li][/ul]
[center][b]Update Log[/b][/center] [code]8/14: Posted Topic and started to work on a smithing handler. 8/15: Worked on the Cook's Assistant quest.[/code]
[center][b]Pictures[/b][/center] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/2ajyq9y.png[/img]
